    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The study or investigation of abnormality, malfunction, or disease. In conservation, the term may be used to describe afflictions to which artifacts are subject, as in "paper pathology".</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
